	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedSecret&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedGoldenChest&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;bombBum&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/ItemPools&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;How you can see here is defined the item pool of your mod item&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;For example&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;treasure&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;Item Id=&quot;513&quot; Weight=&quot;1&quot; DecreaseBy=&quot;0.5&quot; RemoveOn=&quot;0.1&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/Pool&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Name&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Where your item can be found&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;ID of your item&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;content/items.xml&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;items gfxroot=&quot;gfx/items/&quot; version=&quot;1&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;active description=&quot;description of active item&quot; gfx=&quot;Your-image-in-gfx-folder.png&quot; name=&quot;Name of item&quot; id=&quot;your id&quot; maxcharges=&quot;4&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/items&amp;gt;\r///n&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.1518%;&quot;&gt;id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.8482%;&quot;&gt;from 511 to idk what max can be id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.1518%;&quot;&gt;maxcharges&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.8482%;&quot;&gt;there can be 0,1,2,3,4,6,12&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\"\r\n\"state\" \"0\"\r\n\"date\" \"1483656071\"\r\n\"custommenu\" \"\"\r\n\"comments\" \"1\"\r\n\"html\" \"0\"\r\n\"author\" \"1\"\r\n\"oauthor\" \"1\"\r\n\"visiblity\" \"\"\r\n\"tags\" \"LUA,Afterbirth+,Programming,EN\"\r\n', '<p>First you need Afterbirth+</p>\r\n<p>Create folder with your mod name in \"The Binding of Isaac Rebirth\" folder</p>\r\n<p>You need crate file&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">content/items.xml</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Define item</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">resources/gfx/Items/Collectibles/<br />Collectibles_<strong>YourModName</strong>.png</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Icon of active item</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">itempools.xml</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Item pools (here you define where your item can be found in game)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">main.lua</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Main program in LUA to run</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">metadata.xml</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Metadata for steam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>metadata.xml</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\r\n&lt;metadata&gt;\r\n    &lt;name&gt;Mod name&lt;/name&gt;\r\n    &lt;directory&gt;dir_mod&lt;/directory&gt;\r\n    &lt;description&gt;Description of your mod&lt;/description&gt;\r\n    &lt;version&gt;1.0&lt;/version&gt;\r\n    &lt;visibility&gt;Public&lt;/visibility&gt;\r\n    &lt;tag id=\"Active Items\"/&gt;\r\n&lt;/metadata&gt;</code></pre>\r\n<p><strong>itempools.xml</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;ItemPools&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"treasure\"&gt;\r\n		&lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"shop\"&gt;\r\n		&lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"boss\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"devil\"&gt;\r\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"angel\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"secret\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"library\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"challenge\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"goldenChest\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"redChest\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"beggar\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"demonBeggar\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"curse\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"keyMaster\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"bossrush\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"dungeon\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedTreasure\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedBoss\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedShop\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedCurse\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedDevil\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedAngel\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedLibrary\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedSecret\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedGoldenChest\"/&gt;\r\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"bombBum\"/&gt;\r\n&lt;/ItemPools&gt;</code></pre>\r\n<p>How you can see here is defined the item pool of your mod item</p>\r\n<p>For example</p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;Pool Name=\"treasure\"&gt;\r\n    &lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\r\n&lt;/Pool&gt;</code></pre>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Name</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Where your item can be found</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Id</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">ID of your item</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>content/items.xml</strong></p>\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;items gfxroot=\"gfx/items/\" version=\"1\"&gt;\r\n	&lt;active description=\"description of active item\" gfx=\"Your-image-in-gfx-folder.png\" name=\"Name of item\" id=\"your id\" maxcharges=\"4\"/&gt;\r\n&lt;/items&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 48.1518%;\">id</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 48.8482%;\">from 511 to idk what max can be id</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 48.1518%;\">maxcharges</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 48.8482%;\">there can be 0,1,2,3,4,6,12</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'article_5', 'article_history');
