(453, 1, '127.0.0.1', '', 1506721381, '\"id\" \"10\"\r\n\"alias\" \"novy-clanek\"\r\n\"title\" \"Nov&yacute; čl&aacute;nek\"\r\n\"text\" \"&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rick a Morty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;(v anglick&amp;eacute;m origin&amp;aacute;le&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rick and Morty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;) je americk&amp;yacute; animovan&amp;yacute; seri&amp;aacute;l. Jedn&amp;aacute; se o sci-fi komedii pro dospěl&amp;eacute;. Hlavn&amp;iacute;mi postavami jsou vědec Rick, kter&amp;yacute; trp&amp;iacute; alkoholismem a sklony k n&amp;aacute;sil&amp;iacute;, a jeho vnuk Morty, často zvan&amp;yacute; &quot;idiot&quot;, kter&amp;yacute; nen&amp;iacute; zdaleka tak chytr&amp;yacute; a m&amp;aacute; působit jako maskov&amp;aacute;n&amp;iacute;. D&amp;aacute;le tak&amp;eacute; jejich rodina (sestra Summer, otec a matka, kteř&amp;iacute; jsou velmi mlad&amp;iacute;)&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;Seri&amp;aacute;l m&amp;aacute; tři s&amp;eacute;rie. Prvn&amp;iacute; s&amp;eacute;rie vych&amp;aacute;zela v letech&amp;nbsp;2013&amp;nbsp;až&amp;nbsp;2014&amp;nbsp;a obsahuje jeden&amp;aacute;ct epizod. Druh&amp;aacute; s&amp;eacute;rie vy&amp;scaron;la v roce&amp;nbsp;2015&amp;nbsp;a obsahuje 10 epizod. Prvn&amp;iacute; d&amp;iacute;l třet&amp;iacute; s&amp;eacute;rie vy&amp;scaron;el 1. dubna 2017, což měl b&amp;yacute;t apr&amp;iacute;lov&amp;yacute; žert, neboť dal&amp;scaron;&amp;iacute; d&amp;iacute;ly vy&amp;scaron;ly až v l&amp;eacute;tě. Každ&amp;aacute; epizoda m&amp;aacute; okolo 22 minut.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;height: 117px; width: 439px;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 59px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sez&amp;oacute;na&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 65px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Epizody&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 147px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prvn&amp;iacute; epizoda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 140px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Posledn&amp;iacute; epizoda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 59px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: #3366ff; color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 65px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;11&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 147px;&quot;&gt;Prosinec&amp;nbsp;2,&amp;nbsp;2013&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 140px;&quot;&gt;Srpen&amp;nbsp;14,&amp;nbsp;2014&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 59px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: #0000ff; color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 65px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;10&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 147px;&quot;&gt;Červenec&amp;nbsp;26,&amp;nbsp;2015&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 140px;&quot;&gt;Ř&amp;iacute;jen&amp;nbsp;4,&amp;nbsp;2015&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 59px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: #000080; color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 65px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;10&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 147px;&quot;&gt;Srpen&amp;nbsp;1,&amp;nbsp;2017&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 140px;&quot;&gt;Ř&amp;iacute;jen&amp;nbsp;1,&amp;nbsp;2017&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\"\r\n\"state\" \"5\"\r\n\"date\" \"1506721353\"\r\n\"custommenu\" \"\"\r\n\"comments\" \"1\"\r\n\"html\" \"0\"\r\n\"author\" \"1\"\r\n\"oauthor\" \"1\"\r\n\"visiblity\" \"\"\r\n\"tags\" \"\"\r\n\"category\" \"1\"\r\n', '<p><em><strong>Rick a Morty</strong></em>&nbsp;(v anglick&eacute;m origin&aacute;le&nbsp;<em><strong>Rick and Morty</strong></em>) je americk&yacute; animovan&yacute; seri&aacute;l. 