(585, 1, '127.0.0.1', '', 1542400807, '\"id\" \"17\"\r\n\"mid\" \"0\"\r\n\"alias\" \"autoskola-help-2\"\r\n\"title\" \"N&aacute;pověda\"\r\n\"text\" \"&lt;h2 class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;M&amp;iacute;sto kon&amp;aacute;n&amp;iacute; j&amp;iacute;zd&lt;/h2&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;Každ&amp;aacute; j&amp;iacute;zda a sezn&amp;aacute;men&amp;iacute; s vozidlem (pokud nen&amp;iacute; s učitelem dohodnuto jinak) zač&amp;iacute;n&amp;aacute; v bl&amp;iacute;zkosti centra města Ostravy, protože z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;eacute; zkou&amp;scaron;ka z j&amp;iacute;zd zač&amp;iacute;n&amp;aacute; tak&amp;eacute; v centru Ostravy: u nov&amp;eacute; radnice na Proke&amp;scaron;ově n&amp;aacute;měst&amp;iacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;J&amp;iacute;zda tedy&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;okamžitě pokr&amp;yacute;v&amp;aacute; možn&amp;eacute; trasy j&amp;iacute;zd, kter&amp;eacute; budou na z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;eacute; zkou&amp;scaron;ce&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;S t&amp;iacute;mto syst&amp;eacute;mem m&amp;aacute;me velmi&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;pozitivn&amp;iacute; zku&amp;scaron;enosti&lt;/strong&gt;. Tento syst&amp;eacute;m&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;zvy&amp;scaron;uje &amp;uacute;spě&amp;scaron;nost na z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;yacute;ch zkou&amp;scaron;k&amp;aacute;ch&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kde se bude j&amp;iacute;zda konat:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;amp;num=1&amp;amp;t=h&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;amp;spn=0.003042,0.008256&amp;amp;z=14&amp;amp;output=embed&quot; width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; data-mce-fragment=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;amp;num=1&amp;amp;t=h&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;amp;spn=0.003042,0.008256&amp;amp;z=14&amp;amp;source=embed&quot; target=&quot;_new&quot;&gt;Zvět&amp;scaron;it mapu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p class=&quot;next&quot;&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Dal&amp;scaron;&amp;iacute; strana&quot; href=&quot;../../../../autoskola/help/3/&quot;&gt;POKRAČOVAT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;Tuto n&amp;aacute;povědu lze kdykoliv znovu zobrazit stisknut&amp;iacute;m tlač&amp;iacute;tka &amp;ldquo;N&amp;aacute;pověda&amp;rdquo; v lev&amp;eacute;m horn&amp;iacute;m rohu&lt;/p&gt;\"\r\n\"state\" \"5\"\r\n\"date\" \"1535474082\"\r\n\"custommenu\" \"\"\r\n\"comments\" \"1\"\r\n\"html\" \"0\"\r\n\"author\" \"1\"\r\n\"oauthor\" \"1\"\r\n\"visiblity\" \"\"\r\n\"tags\" \"\"\r\n\"category\" \"1\"\r\n\"language\" \"\"\r\n', '<h2 class=\"blue\">M&iacute;sto kon&aacute;n&iacute; j&iacute;zd</h2>\n<p>Každ&aacute; j&iacute;zda a sezn&aacute;men&iacute; s vozidlem (pokud nen&iacute; s učitelem dohodnuto jinak) zač&iacute;n&aacute; v bl&iacute;zkosti centra města Ostravy, protože z&aacute;věrečn&eacute; zkou&scaron;ka z j&iacute;zd zač&iacute;n&aacute; tak&eacute; v centru Ostravy: u nov&eacute; radnice na Proke&scaron;ově n&aacute;měst&iacute;.</p>\n<p>J&iacute;zda tedy&nbsp;<strong>okamžitě pokr&yacute;v&aacute; možn&eacute; trasy j&iacute;zd, kter&eacute; budou na z&aacute;věrečn&eacute; zkou&scaron;ce</strong>.</p>\n<p>S t&iacute;mto syst&eacute;mem m&aacute;me velmi&nbsp;<strong>pozitivn&iacute; zku&scaron;enosti</strong>. Tento syst&eacute;m&nbsp;<strong>zvy&scaron;uje &uacute;spě&scaron;nost na z&aacute;věrečn&yacute;ch zkou&scaron;k&aacute;ch</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Kde se bude j&iacute;zda konat:</strong></p>\n<p><strong><iframe src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;num=1&amp;t=h&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;spn=0.003042,0.008256&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed\" width=\"425\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe><br /><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;num=1&amp;t=h&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;spn=0.003042,0.008256&amp;z=14&amp;source=embed\" target=\"_new\">Zvět&scaron;it mapu</a></strong></p>\n<p class=\"next\"><a title=\"Dal&scaron;&iacute; strana\" href=\"../../../../autoskola/help/3/\">POKRAČOVAT</a></p>\n<p>Tuto n&aacute;povědu lze kdykoliv znovu zobrazit stisknut&iacute;m tlač&iacute;tka &ldquo;N&aacute;pověda&rdquo; v lev&eacute;m horn&iacute;m rohu</p>', 'article_17', 'article_concept'),
