(587, 1, '127.0.0.1', '', 1542473633, '\"id\" \"5\"\r\n\"mid\" \"0\"\r\n\"alias\" \"creating-mod-for-AB-plus-1\"\r\n\"title\" \"Creating mod for Afterbirth+\"\r\n\"text\" \"&lt;p&gt;First you need Afterbirth+&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;Create folder with your mod name in &quot;The Binding of Isaac Rebirth&quot; folder&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;You need crate file&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.7224%;&quot;&gt;content/items.xml&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 66.1547%;&quot;&gt;Define item&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.7224%;&quot;&gt;resources/gfx/Items/Collectibles/&lt;br /&gt;Collectibles_&lt;strong&gt;YourModName&lt;/strong&gt;.png&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 66.1547%;&quot;&gt;Icon of active item&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.7224%;&quot;&gt;itempools.xml&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 66.1547%;&quot;&gt;Item pools (here you define where your item can be found in game)&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.7224%;&quot;&gt;main.lua&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 66.1547%;&quot;&gt;Main program in LUA to run&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.7224%;&quot;&gt;metadata.xml&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 66.1547%;&quot;&gt;Metadata for steam&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;metadata.xml&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;metadata&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;Mod name&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;directory&amp;gt;dir_mod&amp;lt;/directory&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;description&amp;gt;Description of your mod&amp;lt;/description&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;1.0&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;visibility&amp;gt;Public&amp;lt;/visibility&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;tag id=&quot;Active Items&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/metadata&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;itempools.xml&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;ItemPools&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;treasure&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n		&amp;lt;Item Id=&quot;513&quot; Weight=&quot;1&quot; DecreaseBy=&quot;0.5&quot; RemoveOn=&quot;0.1&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;/Pool&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;shop&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n		&amp;lt;Item Id=&quot;513&quot; Weight=&quot;1&quot; DecreaseBy=&quot;0.5&quot; RemoveOn=&quot;0.1&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;/Pool&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;boss&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;devil&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;/Pool&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;angel&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;secret&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;library&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;challenge&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;goldenChest&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;redChest&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;beggar&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;demonBeggar&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;curse&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;keyMaster&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;bossrush&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;dungeon&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedTreasure&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedBoss&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedShop&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedCurse&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedDevil&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedAngel&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedLibrary&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedSecret&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;greedGoldenChest&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;bombBum&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/ItemPools&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;How you can see here is defined the item pool of your mod item&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;For example&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;Pool Name=&quot;treasure&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n    &amp;lt;Item Id=&quot;513&quot; Weight=&quot;1&quot; DecreaseBy=&quot;0.5&quot; RemoveOn=&quot;0.1&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/Pool&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Name&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Where your item can be found&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;Id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 50.0000%;&quot;&gt;ID of your item&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;content/items.xml&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;items gfxroot=&quot;gfx/items/&quot; version=&quot;1&quot;&amp;gt;\r///n	&amp;lt;active description=&quot;description of active item&quot; gfx=&quot;Your-image-in-gfx-folder.png&quot; name=&quot;Name of item&quot; id=&quot;your id&quot; maxcharges=&quot;4&quot;/&amp;gt;\r///n&amp;lt;/items&amp;gt;\r///n&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r///n&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r///n&lt;tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.1518%;&quot;&gt;id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.8482%;&quot;&gt;from 511 to idk what max can be id&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;tr&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.1518%;&quot;&gt;maxcharges&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;td style=&quot;width: 48.8482%;&quot;&gt;there can be 0,1,2,3,4,6,12&lt;/td&gt;\r///n&lt;/tr&gt;\r///n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r///n&lt;/table&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is all for this time. You now know how mods folder is looked.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;[form id=&quot;4&quot;]&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; Prev |&amp;nbsp;&lt;a title=&quot;Next &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&quot; href=&quot;creating-mod-for-AB-plus-2&quot;&gt;Next &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\"\r\n\"state\" \"0\"\r\n\"date\" \"1483656071\"\r\n\"custommenu\" \"\"\r\n\"comments\" \"1\"\r\n\"html\" \"0\"\r\n\"author\" \"1\"\r\n\"oauthor\" \"1\"\r\n\"visiblity\" \"\"\r\n\"tags\" \"LUA,Afterbirth+,Programming,EN\"\r\n\"category\" \"0\"\r\n\"language\" \"\"\r\n', '<p>First you need Afterbirth+</p>\n<p>Create folder with your mod name in \"The Binding of Isaac Rebirth\" folder</p>\n<p>You need crate file&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">content/items.xml</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Define item</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">resources/gfx/Items/Collectibles/<br />Collectibles_<strong>YourModName</strong>.png</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Icon of active item</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">itempools.xml</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Item pools (here you define where your item can be found in game)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">main.lua</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Main program in LUA to run</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.7224%;\">metadata.xml</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.1547%;\">Metadata for steam</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>metadata.xml</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n&lt;metadata&gt;\n    &lt;name&gt;Mod name&lt;/name&gt;\n    &lt;directory&gt;dir_mod&lt;/directory&gt;\n    &lt;description&gt;Description of your mod&lt;/description&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.0&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;visibility&gt;Public&lt;/visibility&gt;\n    &lt;tag id=\"Active Items\"/&gt;\n&lt;/metadata&gt;</code></pre>\n<p><strong>itempools.xml</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;ItemPools&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"treasure\"&gt;\n		&lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"shop\"&gt;\n		&lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"boss\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"devil\"&gt;\n	&lt;/Pool&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"angel\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"secret\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"library\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"challenge\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"goldenChest\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"redChest\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"beggar\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"demonBeggar\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"curse\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"keyMaster\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"bossrush\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"dungeon\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedTreasure\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedBoss\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedShop\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedCurse\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedDevil\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedAngel\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedLibrary\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedSecret\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"greedGoldenChest\"/&gt;\n	&lt;Pool Name=\"bombBum\"/&gt;\n&lt;/ItemPools&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>How you can see here is defined the item pool of your mod item</p>\n<p>For example</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>&lt;Pool Name=\"treasure\"&gt;\n    &lt;Item Id=\"513\" Weight=\"1\" DecreaseBy=\"0.5\" RemoveOn=\"0.1\"/&gt;\n&lt;/Pool&gt;</code></pre>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Name</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Where your item can be found</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">Id</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.0000%;\">ID of your item</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><s