(607, 1, '127.0.0.1', '', 1550502544, '\"id\" \"17\"\r\n\"mid\" \"0\"\r\n\"alias\" \"autoskola-help-2\"\r\n\"title\" \"N&aacute;pověda\"\r\n\"text\" \"&lt;h2 class=&quot;blue&quot;&gt;M&amp;iacute;sto kon&amp;aacute;n&amp;iacute; j&amp;iacute;zd&lt;/h2&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;Každ&amp;aacute; j&amp;iacute;zda a sezn&amp;aacute;men&amp;iacute; s vozidlem (pokud nen&amp;iacute; s učitelem dohodnuto jinak) zač&amp;iacute;n&amp;aacute; v bl&amp;iacute;zkosti centra města Ostravy, protože z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;eacute; zkou&amp;scaron;ka z j&amp;iacute;zd zač&amp;iacute;n&amp;aacute; tak&amp;eacute; v centru Ostravy: u nov&amp;eacute; radnice na Proke&amp;scaron;ově n&amp;aacute;měst&amp;iacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;J&amp;iacute;zda tedy&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;okamžitě pokr&amp;yacute;v&amp;aacute; možn&amp;eacute; trasy j&amp;iacute;zd, kter&amp;eacute; budou na z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;eacute; zkou&amp;scaron;ce&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;S t&amp;iacute;mto syst&amp;eacute;mem m&amp;aacute;me velmi&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;pozitivn&amp;iacute; zku&amp;scaron;enosti&lt;/strong&gt;. Tento syst&amp;eacute;m&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;zvy&amp;scaron;uje &amp;uacute;spě&amp;scaron;nost na z&amp;aacute;věrečn&amp;yacute;ch zkou&amp;scaron;k&amp;aacute;ch&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kde se bude j&amp;iacute;zda konat:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r///n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;amp;num=1&amp;amp;t=h&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;amp;spn=0.003042,0.008256&amp;amp;z=14&amp;amp;output=embed&quot; width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; data-mce-fragment=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maps.google.com/maps?q=49.83045,18.274228&amp;amp;num=1&amp;amp;t=h&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;ll=49.830066,18.274443&amp;amp;spn=0.003042,0.